  "title": "AMAKURU IJYANYE NA MIFEM",
  "summary": "MIFEM ni ihuriro cyangwa igice cy’itorero ry’Abadventiste b’Umunsi wa Karindwi (SDA) kigizwe n’abagore n’abakobwa, bishyize hamwe mu murimo w’ivugabutumwa. Bashyigikirwa n’abasaza n’abavandimwe babo mu itorero, bagafashanya gukura mu buryo bw’umwuka no kwamamaza ubutumwa bwiza.Muri rusana, MIFEM igizwe n'amagambo ahinnye asobanura: \"Umurimo w'Umugore n'Umukobwa batewe ingabo mu bitugu na basaza babo beguriye impagarike yabo Umwami wabo.\"Dore amakuru n'inshingano by'ingenzi biyiranga:Ivugabutumwa: Bakora ibikorwa bitandukanye by’ivugabutumwa mu muryango ndetse no hanze y’itorero, nk’uko n’andi matsinda abikora.MIFEM Junior: Ni igice cy’abana n’abangavu aho batozwa gukurira mu nzira z’Imana bakiri bato (bishingiye ku ntego yo mu Migani 22:6).Kongere n'Imiherero: Itegura amateraniro n'amahugurwa ajyanye no kwigisha abagore n'abakobwa kugira uruhare mu iterambere ry'itorero n'umuryango mugari",
